# User Uploads
# Ignore product images (IDs), but keep core assets if needed.
# Typically, for simplicity:
/img/[0-9]*.jpg
/img/[0-9]*.png
/img/[0-9]*.jpeg

# If you want to ignore ALL images except specific assets:
# /img/*
# !/img/logo.jpg
# !/img/background.jpg
# ...

